**Core Responsibilities:**

- Customer first mentality
- Service, nurture and grow your portfolio
- Educate customers on best practice within their product mix
- Manage the full life cycle of campaigns, including onboarding, growing, and retaining
- Manage a large volume of inbound/outbound calls each day

**Experience Required:**

- Previous experience in account management in a high volume phone based role
- Ability to work autonomously with support that is not face to face
- Familiarity with Salesforce highly advantageous
- Exposure to online marketing or advertising is an advantage
- Capability to not only service customers but continue their growth
- Aptitude in utilising data within your recommendations

**Keywords**:

- Account Management
- Customer service
- Portfolio growth
- Customer education
- Campaign management
- Inbound/outbound calls management
- Salesforce
- Online marketing
- Advertising
- Data utilisation
- Autonomous work
- Non-face to face support.
